# Project: Bubblepi Store

Platform jual beli akun digital (e.g. Capcut Pro, Canva Pro, dll) dengan sistem garansi, supplier otomatis, dan pembayaran via Xendit.

## Stack

| Layer         | Tool                                    |
| ------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| Language      | TypeScript (Node.js)                    |
| Frontend      | Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19      |
| Backend       | Next.js Server Actions + API Routes     |
| Database      | PostgreSQL                              |
| ORM           | Prisma 6                                |
| Auth          | JWT (jose) + Xendit webhook             |
| Styling       | Tailwind CSS v4 + shadcn/ui (base-nova) |
| Package mgr   | pnpm                                    |
| Deployment    | (TBD — konfigurasi production)          |
| Email         | Resend + React Email                    |
| Payment       | Xendit (QRIS, Virtual Account)          |
| Testing       | node:test + node:assert                 |

## Path Conventions

- **App Routes:** `app/` (App Router)
- **API Routes:** `app/api/`
- **Pages (Store):** `app/(store)/`
- **Pages (Dashboard):** `app/(dashboard)/`
- **Admin Pages:** `app/admin/`
- **Components:** `components/`
  - UI primitives: `components/ui/`
  - Store-specific: `components/store/`
  - Admin-specific: `components/admin/`
  - Product-related: `components/product/`
  - Order-related: `components/order/`
  - Checkout: `components/checkout/`
- **Server Logic:** `lib/`
  - Auth: `lib/auth.ts`, `lib/admin-auth.ts`
  - Payment: `lib/xendit.ts`
  - Database: `lib/db.ts`
  - Utilities: `lib/utils.ts`, `lib/validators.ts`
  - Suppliers: `lib/suppliers/`
  - Stock: `lib/stock.ts`
  - Email: `lib/mailer.ts`
- **Prisma Schema:** `prisma/schema.prisma`
- **Cron Scripts:** `scripts/`
- **Cron API Endpoints:** `app/api/cron/`
- **Tests:** `tests/`

## Environment

- Semua secrets di env vars, tidak di source code
- `DATABASE_URL` — PostgreSQL connection string
- `XENDIT_*` — Xendit payment gateway credentials
- `RESEND_API_KEY` — Resend email service
- `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` atau JWT secret (via jose)
- `TELEGRAM_*` — Telegram bot credentials (supplier integration)